title: LOL! DJ Fresh pokes fun at illuminati accusations
text:
WATCH: Babes and Cassper bring all the moves in new music video 
These rumours aren't new and have plagued Fresh like a bad rash for years. 
However, the radio jock has no time to entertain the rumours, and instead uses the claims as a form of entertainment. 
In the latest incident, a fake Trevor Noah Facebook page shared a list of SA celebrities who have apparently been linked to the illuminati. WATCH: Babes and Cassper bring all the moves in new music video 
The headline of the post read: "My heart broke when I saw the list of SA celebrities who sold their souls to the devil!" 
Fresh shared a screenshot of the post with a rather amusing caption. "#MamaIMadeIt Though coz I work In radio, I struck myself as more of a #Khulumanathi (talk to us) member!! Oh well!!! *Shrugs*," he said.
